104
00:05:25.715 --> 00:05:28.010
50, 60, 70, 80,

105
00:05:28.010 --> 00:05:32.195
bullet points about
you say this here,

106
00:05:32.195 --> 00:05:34.925
how do you know that, back it up,

107
00:05:34.925 --> 00:05:37.670
scale back, take it out,

108
00:05:37.670 --> 00:05:40.550
all these claims I want to make,

109
00:05:40.550 --> 00:05:43.430
they are holding
me to task saying,

110
00:05:43.430 --> 00:05:45.590
you back this up or
you take it out,

111
00:05:45.590 --> 00:05:46.880
or you scale it back,

112
00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:48.830
and I respond to all that.

113
00:05:48.830 --> 00:05:50.180
So I see all these bullet points.

114
00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:53.435
I send a new one,
they look at that.

115
00:05:53.435 --> 00:05:55.130
More bullet points
back and forth,

116
00:05:55.130 --> 00:05:57.350
could happen four or
five times. All right.

117
00:05:57.350 --> 00:06:00.125
So, the document that

